'''Richard Mills''' was a sculptor who worked on [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']].<ref name="Episode 1 Crew List">{{SWArchive|url=episode-i/bts/castcrew.html|text=''The Phantom Menace'' Cast and Crew}}</ref> He worked as an electrician and rigger for [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']].<ref name="Episode 3 Crew List">{{SWArchive|url=episode-iii/castcrew.html|text=Episode III Cast & Crew}}</ref>

